caption: ⚡💫 Neon rain pours down the alleys of NeoCity, and Jaxara, the daring cyberpunk siren, laces her silhouette in a daring low‑angle, backlit shot that captures her bold confidence. She struts through neon‑lit streets, leaving holographic trails of glittering neon signs in her wake, as she sprints past the rainy streets of the city, leaving a trail of electric charm that makes her the night star of the digital streets. #cyberpunk #futurism #streetfashion #digitalart #neonaesthetics
